### User Data Deletion
Users have the right to request the deletion of their data collected through our app.

To request data deletion:
1. Email us at [your-email@example.com] with the subject "Data Deletion Request."
2. Provide your username or the email address associated with your account.

We will process your request within [X days] and confirm when your data has been deleted.

Please note: Some data may need to be retained for legal or regulatory purposes.